1
00:00:29,210 --> 00:00:30,090
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font size="40"><font color="#2d1508">Hell's Paradise</font></font></b></font>

2
00:00:30,130 --> 00:00:35,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A faint flower was blooming 
unnoticed by anyone</i></font>

3
00:00:35,490 --> 00:00:40,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not a burning red, 
but flickering serenely in red</i></font>

4
00:00:40,490 --> 00:00:45,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've been pausing for a long time 
dragging my past at my feet</i></font>

5
00:00:45,840 --> 00:00:48,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I break free from this ambivalence,</i></font>

6
00:00:48,440 --> 00:00:51,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>will I be able to bloom by its side?</i></font>

7
00:00:51,850 --> 00:00:54,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The future is slipping away 
between my fingers</i></font>

8
00:00:54,490 --> 00:00:57,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What mistake did I make 
to pay this price?</i></font>

9
00:00:57,010 --> 00:01:01,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Always hurting myself</i></font>

10
00:01:01,860 --> 00:01:07,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and hesitant even to a small joy</i></font>

11
00:01:07,720 --> 00:01:09,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to stop now</i></font>

12
00:01:09,410 --> 00:01:11,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The flower just bloomed in dignity</i></font>

13
00:01:11,930 --> 00:01:14,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and that was all I needed to be happy</i></font>

14
00:01:14,550 --> 00:01:19,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I just wanted to protect this one flower</i></font>

15
00:01:19,670 --> 00:01:22,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wishing to be strong, I</i></font>

16
00:01:22,380 --> 00:01:25,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>picked up the vulnerability 
I had once cast away</i></font>

17
00:01:25,040 --> 00:01:26,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Can't break free from the ambivalence</i></font>

18
00:01:26,990 --> 00:01:30,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In ambivalence, I become myself</i></font>

19
00:01:30,180 --> 00:01:32,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Like rooting strongly into the soil</i></font>

20
00:01:32,890 --> 00:01:35,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>like swaying ephemerally to the wind</i></font>

21
00:01:35,440 --> 00:01:38,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm slowly loosening myself to bloom</i></font>

22
00:01:38,530 --> 00:01:41,660
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font size="40">Hell's Paradise</font></b></font>

23
00:01:45,950 --> 00:01:52,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So depending on the matchup, 
it may make sense for me to protect you.</font>

24
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:52,010
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>Ephemeralness and Fire</b></font>

25
00:01:53,460 --> 00:01:58,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're both shinobi, 
but you and I are nothing alike.</font>

26
00:01:58,620 --> 00:02:01,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing's more important 
to me than my life.</font>

27
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:04,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not risking it for anything.</font>

28
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I agree.</font>

29
00:02:06,430 --> 00:02:08,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My goal is to make it back home alive.</font>

30
00:02:08,900 --> 00:02:11,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To live and see my wife.</font>

31
00:02:12,170 --> 00:02:14,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't intend to risk my life.</font>

32
00:02:15,510 --> 00:02:17,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enough.</font>

33
00:02:44,440 --> 00:02:47,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mission complete. Let's get out of here.</font>

34
00:02:48,540 --> 00:02:50,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't leave anything behind.</font>

35
00:02:50,010 --> 00:02:51,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gabimaru.</font>

36
00:02:51,570 --> 00:02:53,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've been acting strange.</font>

37
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:56,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've stopped killing on every job.</font>

38
00:02:59,500 --> 00:03:04,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You used to kill everyone in the way 
before getting to work.</font>

39
00:03:04,460 --> 00:03:07,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What does it matter? 
We were hired to steal this.</font>

40
00:03:07,690 --> 00:03:09,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that it?</font>

41
00:03:09,460 --> 00:03:11,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Has getting married changed your thinking?</font>

42
00:03:14,850 --> 00:03:18,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A mere marriage wouldn't 
cause a change of heart.</i></font>

43
00:03:20,870 --> 00:03:23,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, welcome home.</font>

44
00:03:26,100 --> 00:03:28,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">D-Darling.</font>

45
00:03:28,670 --> 00:03:31,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, yeah.</font>

46
00:03:31,220 --> 00:03:33,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not hurt today.</font>

47
00:03:33,940 --> 00:03:35,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm relieved.</font>

48
00:03:35,660 --> 00:03:41,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">L-Lately, I haven't been 
hired to kill anyone.</font>

49
00:03:41,780 --> 00:03:43,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

50
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:46,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's good.</font>

51
00:03:48,190 --> 00:03:49,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad.</font>

52
00:03:51,640 --> 00:03:53,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's not a change of heart.</i></font>

53
00:03:53,590 --> 00:03:55,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm at a loss.</i></font>

54
00:03:55,570 --> 00:04:00,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My whole life, I've only lived 
as a shinobi, and yet...</i></font>

55
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:04,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't know how to face her.</i></font>

56
00:04:09,660 --> 00:04:14,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I like chestnut rice.</font>

57
00:04:14,260 --> 00:04:16,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Oh...</font>

58
00:04:16,280 --> 00:04:17,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

59
00:04:18,260 --> 00:04:20,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't know how to face her.</i></font>

60
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:24,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, what is it this time?</font>

61
00:04:25,540 --> 00:04:27,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Killing.</font>

62
00:04:27,540 --> 00:04:30,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Gabimaru the Hollow, 
without blood or tears.</i></font>

63
00:04:30,280 --> 00:04:33,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That is my true face.</i></font>

64
00:04:36,080 --> 00:04:37,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome...</font>

65
00:04:38,980 --> 00:04:40,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay where you are.</font>

66
00:04:41,070 --> 00:04:42,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My face looks awful.</font>

67
00:04:43,350 --> 00:04:44,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd only scare you.</font>

68
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:51,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop.</font>

69
00:04:52,450 --> 00:04:54,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll be soiled.</font>

70
00:04:59,820 --> 00:05:03,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You're not afraid?</font>

71
00:05:03,410 --> 00:05:05,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course not.</font>

72
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:09,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not an ogre or a ghost.</font>

73
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:13,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whatever your face looks like, 
you're still my husband.</font>

74
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:22,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I still don't know how to face her.</i></font>

75
00:05:23,490 --> 00:05:28,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I don't ever want 
her expression to be clouded.</i></font>

76
00:05:29,390 --> 00:05:30,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yui...</i></font>

77
00:05:44,440 --> 00:05:47,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My goal is to live and see my wife.</font>

78
00:05:48,580 --> 00:05:51,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't intend to risk my life.</font>

79
00:05:52,870 --> 00:05:54,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So...</font>

80
00:05:56,460 --> 00:05:58,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll risk everything else instead.</font>

81
00:06:03,690 --> 00:06:05,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My beliefs.</font>

82
00:06:06,180 --> 00:06:08,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My reason, my common sense.</font>

83
00:06:10,050 --> 00:06:11,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even my humanity.</font>

84
00:06:44,190 --> 00:06:47,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gabimaru probably using plan B.</font>

85
00:06:45,470 --> 00:06:47,970
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#af321b"><font size="15">Gabimaru</font></font></b></font>

86
00:06:45,470 --> 00:06:47,970
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b><font color="#b0231f">{\an8}Yuzuriha</font></b></font>

87
00:06:47,970 --> 00:06:50,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Plan B?</font>

88
00:06:51,400 --> 00:06:56,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When human and flower merge, human 
turns into flower if flower's tao wins.</font>

89
00:06:56,890 --> 00:07:01,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if balanced, 
human gains flower's power.</font>

90
00:07:01,980 --> 00:07:04,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just like Tensen.</font>

91
00:07:06,420 --> 00:07:08,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what my brother did.</font>

92
00:07:08,090 --> 00:07:11,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, but he beat flower's tao.</font>

93
00:07:11,990 --> 00:07:14,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tan entered body through flower,</font>

94
00:07:14,660 --> 00:07:20,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but only very small amount, 
so achieved balance.</font>

95
00:07:20,420 --> 00:07:23,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His body same as Tensen now.</font>

96
00:07:23,700 --> 00:07:26,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In other words, if we control 
the transformation,</font>

97
00:07:26,430 --> 00:07:29,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we can regenerate just like them.</font>

98
00:07:30,310 --> 00:07:32,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's something 
I'd like to confirm.</font>

99
00:07:34,290 --> 00:07:35,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mu Dan's tentacle.</font>

100
00:07:36,350 --> 00:07:38,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can use this to turn 
myself into flowers.</font>

101
00:07:39,260 --> 00:07:41,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It should be easy to control this little.</font>

102
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:42,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Too dangerous.</font>

103
00:07:43,190 --> 00:07:44,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Balance happens by coincidence.</font>

104
00:07:44,940 --> 00:07:48,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Normally, turn into flower, 
even if small amount.</font>

105
00:07:48,150 --> 00:07:50,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Chobe did it.</font>

106
00:07:52,650 --> 00:07:53,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How?</font>

107
00:07:55,280 --> 00:07:58,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Probably because on verge of death.</font>

108
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:06,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tao consumed by breathing, thinking, 
everything involved in living.</font>

109
00:08:07,590 --> 00:08:12,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But when dying, do nothing. No thoughts.</font>

110
00:08:12,280 --> 00:08:17,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So tao focus only on regenerating.</font>

111
00:08:17,830 --> 00:08:18,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

112
00:08:18,980 --> 00:08:20,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No see!</font>

113
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:22,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brother special.</font>

114
00:08:22,590 --> 00:08:25,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Beat flower's tao even when unconscious.</font>

115
00:08:25,630 --> 00:08:27,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sense of self strong.</font>

116
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Desire to live strong.</font>

117
00:08:28,960 --> 00:08:32,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My brother is special. Give it up.</font>

118
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:34,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll just end up like the others.</font>

119
00:08:34,740 --> 00:08:38,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you stab yourself with that, 
you'll turn into a flower and die.</font>

120
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:43,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chobe was different from the others 
because he had something to lose.</font>

121
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:50,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because he had someone to live for,</font>

122
00:08:51,550 --> 00:08:53,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">no matter what it cost him.</font>

123
00:08:54,130 --> 00:08:58,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Abandon humanity to make it home alive.</font>

124
00:08:59,150 --> 00:09:00,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That is...</font>

125
00:09:00,560 --> 00:09:02,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Plan B.</font>

126
00:09:04,060 --> 00:09:05,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It defies common sense.</font>

127
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:13,450
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#af321b"><font size="15">Gabimaru</font></font></b></font>

128
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:13,450
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b><font color="#b0231f">{\an8}Yuzuriha</font></b></font>

129
00:09:07,640 --> 00:09:10,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Gabimaru could do it.</font>

130
00:09:11,100 --> 00:09:13,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I'm sure he will</font>

131
00:09:13,740 --> 00:09:18,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">if that will get him closer to his wife.</font>

132
00:09:31,130 --> 00:09:35,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Gaining the ability to regenerate 
hasn't changed much.</i></font>

133
00:09:39,270 --> 00:09:41,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My opponent hinders me.</i></font>

134
00:09:42,230 --> 00:09:44,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My regeneration and tao 
are being weakened.</i></font>

135
00:09:44,900 --> 00:09:47,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My endurance has only increased slightly.</i></font>

136
00:09:48,400 --> 00:09:54,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We both have to avoid fatal blows 
to our tanden in particular.</i></font>

137
00:09:54,160 --> 00:09:56,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But that's all it would take.</i></font>

138
00:09:56,280 --> 00:09:58,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That would be enough...</i></font>

139
00:09:59,160 --> 00:10:00,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>to kill Ran.</i></font>

140
00:10:01,310 --> 00:10:03,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Before my body is consumed by flowers.</i></font>

141
00:10:20,890 --> 00:10:22,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a freak.</font>

142
00:10:22,980 --> 00:10:26,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're still fighting after dying once.</font>

143
00:10:26,810 --> 00:10:28,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've even abandoned your humanity.</font>

144
00:10:30,150 --> 00:10:32,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For an uncertainty.</font>

145
00:10:33,740 --> 00:10:37,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a fool. 
I don't have time for this.</font>

146
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:40,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe you're right.</font>

147
00:10:41,940 --> 00:10:46,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But there are places only fools can reach.</font>

148
00:10:47,380 --> 00:10:49,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Calmness and logic won't get you there.</font>

149
00:10:50,730 --> 00:10:53,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sometimes, you can only 
rely on your experiences.</font>

150
00:10:54,150 --> 00:10:56,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're self-serving, 
but you're also clear-headed.</font>

151
00:10:56,870 --> 00:11:00,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've probably never known 
anything that's made you a fool.</font>

152
00:11:03,540 --> 00:11:06,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You bet I'm clear-headed.</font>

153
00:11:06,010 --> 00:11:08,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't fight anyone I can't beat.</font>

154
00:11:13,540 --> 00:11:14,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

155
00:11:15,970 --> 00:11:20,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll make anyone who tears 
my favorite clothes pay.</font>

156
00:11:20,560 --> 00:11:22,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those aren't even yours.</font>

157
00:11:25,210 --> 00:11:29,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My fire tao can't strike a fatal blow 
against Ran's water tao.</font>

158
00:11:30,090 --> 00:11:33,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But for your earth tao, it'd be possible.</font>

159
00:11:33,090 --> 00:11:37,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't hindering tao ineffective 
if the difference is too great?</font>

160
00:11:38,680 --> 00:11:43,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Plus, unlike Mu Dan, they retain 
their intellect while transformed.</font>

161
00:11:43,060 --> 00:11:46,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not sure any coordinated attack 
we throw together will work.</font>

162
00:11:46,060 --> 00:11:47,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why we have to do it.</font>

163
00:11:50,070 --> 00:11:54,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Honestly, it's a gamble, 
but we don't have a choice.</font>

164
00:11:54,660 --> 00:11:56,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's for my wife.</font>

165
00:11:56,140 --> 00:11:58,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, yes. This again.</font>

166
00:11:58,370 --> 00:12:01,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm kind of relieved you haven't changed 
despite abandoning your humanity.</font>

167
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:08,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ninjutsu! Such impressive 
training and study.</font>

168
00:12:12,710 --> 00:12:14,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ninpo: Demonic Firebug.</i></font>

169
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:18,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ninpo: Pyro Bridge.</i></font>

170
00:12:23,330 --> 00:12:26,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh, I was trying to tear that off.</font>

171
00:12:26,270 --> 00:12:27,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's plenty.</font>

172
00:12:34,550 --> 00:12:36,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ninpo: Ascetic Blaze.</i></font>

173
00:12:48,470 --> 00:12:51,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hot! Move!</font>

174
00:12:55,050 --> 00:12:58,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The result will always be the same.</font>

175
00:12:58,460 --> 00:13:02,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know what you're trying to do.</font>

176
00:13:02,570 --> 00:13:08,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your imperfect teamwork is pointless</font>

177
00:13:08,680 --> 00:13:10,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but beautiful.</font>

178
00:13:11,310 --> 00:13:14,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A desperate battle. Ninjutsu.</font>

179
00:13:14,700 --> 00:13:20,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Refined by imperfect humans, 
the crystallization of kung fu.</font>

180
00:13:20,580 --> 00:13:24,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got plenty more, 
including ones that can kill you.</font>

181
00:13:27,160 --> 00:13:30,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very well. Show me everything you have.</font>

182
00:13:31,130 --> 00:13:33,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is all part of my training.</font>

183
00:13:33,540 --> 00:13:36,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It will feed my doin.</font>

184
00:13:37,800 --> 00:13:40,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you have to provoke them?</font>

185
00:13:40,350 --> 00:13:41,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is fine.</font>

186
00:13:41,800 --> 00:13:44,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the only way we can win.</font>

187
00:13:44,180 --> 00:13:45,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, come on.</font>

188
00:13:45,980 --> 00:13:48,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine, I'll do it.</font>

189
00:14:34,490 --> 00:14:40,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tao consumed by breathing, thinking, 
everything involved in living.</font>

190
00:14:40,650 --> 00:14:43,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Transforming must consume 
a lot of tao as well.</font>

191
00:14:44,090 --> 00:14:48,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In other words, once the transformation 
is dispelled, their tao will be exhausted.</font>

192
00:14:48,890 --> 00:14:51,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They might even have less than us.</font>

193
00:14:51,490 --> 00:14:53,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that true?</font>

194
00:14:53,850 --> 00:14:54,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

195
00:14:56,200 --> 00:14:58,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kishikai use lots of tao.</font>

196
00:14:58,920 --> 00:15:01,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't maintain a whole hour.</font>

197
00:15:01,990 --> 00:15:03,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An hour...</font>

198
00:15:03,340 --> 00:15:05,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a long battle.</font>

199
00:15:09,020 --> 00:15:11,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you done already?</font>

200
00:15:12,660 --> 00:15:15,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I've done enough.</font>

201
00:15:17,800 --> 00:15:22,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know you respond to external stimuli 
the same way humans do.</font>

202
00:15:22,820 --> 00:15:24,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even to light.</font>

203
00:15:26,820 --> 00:15:31,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So extreme flickering should 
temporarily excite your nervous system.</font>

204
00:15:34,340 --> 00:15:36,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excessive focus due to excitement</font>

205
00:15:36,800 --> 00:15:39,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">robs people of their judgment 
and sense of time.</font>

206
00:15:40,210 --> 00:15:43,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's an old trick used by shinobi 
during interrogations.</font>

207
00:15:44,380 --> 00:15:45,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could it be?</font>

208
00:15:45,730 --> 00:15:48,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was buying time and waiting for this.</font>

209
00:15:50,310 --> 00:15:54,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a long battle, but 
if you can hold out for an hour...</font>

210
00:15:55,210 --> 00:15:56,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll have a rare shot at winning.</font>

211
00:15:57,580 --> 00:15:59,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Their transformation will fall apart.</font>

212
00:16:00,530 --> 00:16:04,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After transformation ends, no strength.</font>

213
00:16:05,360 --> 00:16:08,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Normally, we're powerless 
against the god-like Tensen.</font>

214
00:16:09,480 --> 00:16:13,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I'll drag them down to 
a level I can reach.</font>

215
00:16:15,240 --> 00:16:16,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's their actual body's tao.</i></font>

216
00:16:17,360 --> 00:16:18,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now's the time to strike.</i></font>

217
00:16:26,680 --> 00:16:30,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They dispelled the transformation 
before they ran out of tao.</i></font>

218
00:16:32,510 --> 00:16:35,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're restoring their tao 
through circulation.</i></font>

219
00:16:35,720 --> 00:16:36,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuzuriha!</font>

220
00:16:36,770 --> 00:16:39,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Destroy Ran's tanden using hindrance 
before they can recover!</font>

221
00:16:40,150 --> 00:16:42,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She can't.</font>

222
00:16:43,450 --> 00:16:48,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can see that she's severely wounded. 
She can barely stand.</font>

223
00:16:48,960 --> 00:16:52,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If she focuses her tao 
on her weapons, she'll die.</font>

224
00:16:53,730 --> 00:16:57,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's not prepared to risk her life.</font>

225
00:16:58,290 --> 00:17:02,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right. I care about 
myself first and foremost.</font>

226
00:17:03,920 --> 00:17:06,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no point if I die.</font>

227
00:17:07,170 --> 00:17:08,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

228
00:17:09,400 --> 00:17:14,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I'd die from stress 
if I let you live.</font>

229
00:17:15,680 --> 00:17:19,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have to do what I want to do.</font>

230
00:17:19,730 --> 00:17:22,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's more to life 
than breathing, you know?</font>

231
00:17:25,200 --> 00:17:26,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very well.</font>

232
00:17:28,440 --> 00:17:30,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've had enough.</font>

233
00:17:39,790 --> 00:17:43,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have to do what I want to do.</i></font>

234
00:17:58,560 --> 00:18:00,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Breathing isn't all there is.</i></font>

235
00:18:20,520 --> 00:18:23,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-Brother...</font>

236
00:18:27,740 --> 00:18:31,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My poor brother...</font>

237
00:18:36,940 --> 00:18:38,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right?</font>

238
00:18:38,190 --> 00:18:39,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you?</font>

239
00:18:39,850 --> 00:18:42,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've just been pierced by a pillar.</font>

240
00:18:42,580 --> 00:18:44,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not hindering me.</font>

241
00:18:44,660 --> 00:18:46,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll take time, but I can regenerate.</font>

242
00:18:47,610 --> 00:18:50,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's not perfect, right?</font>

243
00:18:50,850 --> 00:18:57,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The more you regenerate, the more 
you'll turn into a flower, like the Hoko.</font>

244
00:18:58,070 --> 00:19:00,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's limited regeneration.</font>

245
00:19:00,620 --> 00:19:02,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it continues 
to consume you, you'll die.</font>

246
00:19:02,750 --> 00:19:05,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An even worse hell 
could be waiting for you.</font>

247
00:19:05,550 --> 00:19:09,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, I had to do this
if I wanted to return to my wife.</font>

248
00:19:09,810 --> 00:19:12,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously, you're astonishing.</font>

249
00:19:12,040 --> 00:19:13,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're fine, then let's go.</font>

250
00:19:13,990 --> 00:19:15,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're joking, right?</font>

251
00:19:15,770 --> 00:19:17,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me rest!</font>

252
00:19:18,130 --> 00:19:19,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no time.</font>

253
00:19:20,150 --> 00:19:22,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll go after Sagiri and Mei.</font>

254
00:19:22,020 --> 00:19:26,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's currently unclear 
who will reach the sluice gate.</font>

255
00:19:26,480 --> 00:19:29,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We may need to get there first.</font>

256
00:19:29,720 --> 00:19:31,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then go without me.</font>

257
00:19:31,770 --> 00:19:33,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll catch up after I rest.</font>

258
00:19:34,440 --> 00:19:36,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure you're okay?</font>

259
00:19:36,610 --> 00:19:40,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you're worried about me? 
I'm surprised.</font>

260
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:41,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If your wife finds out, 
she'll be mad at—</font>

261
00:19:41,580 --> 00:19:44,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's not that petty.</font>

262
00:19:45,140 --> 00:19:48,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm totally fine. Just go.</font>

263
00:19:49,020 --> 00:19:50,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be waiting.</font>

264
00:19:54,470 --> 00:19:55,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuzuriha.</font>

265
00:19:55,440 --> 00:19:56,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

266
00:19:56,380 --> 00:19:57,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What now?</font>

267
00:19:57,530 --> 00:19:59,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for saving me.</font>

268
00:20:00,140 --> 00:20:01,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean it.</font>

269
00:20:10,270 --> 00:20:13,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh, I screwed up.</font>

270
00:20:13,470 --> 00:20:15,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is deep.</font>

271
00:20:17,610 --> 00:20:21,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not like me to get hit.</font>

272
00:20:22,210 --> 00:20:26,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rin-pyo-tou-sha-kai-jin-retsu-zai-zen.</font>

273
00:20:26,570 --> 00:20:30,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I never show anyone how I truly feel.</i></font>

274
00:20:31,220 --> 00:20:36,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll live and die by myself.</i></font>

275
00:20:36,210 --> 00:20:39,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do I need a reason to 
want to make it back alive?</font>

276
00:20:39,220 --> 00:20:43,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm young and don't want to die. 
That's all.</font>

277
00:20:45,680 --> 00:20:48,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sorry, Saya.</i></font>

278
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:54,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Your big sister tried really hard 
to live for the both of us.</i></font>

279
00:20:56,220 --> 00:20:59,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But this might be the end.</font>

280
00:20:59,030 --> 00:21:03,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you're struggling, 
think about things you like.</font>

281
00:21:04,860 --> 00:21:07,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Think only of a pet cat, 
the one you love,</font>

282
00:21:07,980 --> 00:21:12,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">your family, and beautiful sights.</font>

283
00:21:27,860 --> 00:21:29,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How unexpected.</font>

284
00:21:29,570 --> 00:21:33,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's natural 
for incomplete tao to win.</font>

285
00:21:35,300 --> 00:21:37,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where are you going?</font>

286
00:21:37,240 --> 00:21:38,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To report to Rien.</font>

287
00:21:38,990 --> 00:21:41,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should do as you wish.</font>

288
00:21:42,090 --> 00:21:46,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure you should 
be leaving us here?</font>

289
00:21:46,380 --> 00:21:49,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It doesn't matter. 
You said you didn't want to fight.</font>

290
00:21:50,620 --> 00:21:52,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not going to avenge your friend?</font>

291
00:21:52,760 --> 00:21:54,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

292
00:21:54,000 --> 00:21:58,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They were weeded out. 
That's part of our training.</font>

293
00:21:58,000 --> 00:22:01,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That is the way of the sage. 
You know that, Mei.</font>

294
00:22:02,510 --> 00:22:07,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Tensen are truthseekers. 
We have no bonds or feelings.</font>

295
00:22:07,050 --> 00:22:09,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You followed by example, too.</font>

296
00:22:09,850 --> 00:22:14,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After leaving Horai, you hid 
and watched the island decline.</font>

297
00:22:15,110 --> 00:22:17,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did you return now?</font>

298
00:22:19,900 --> 00:22:25,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I finally understood life. Was taught.</font>

299
00:22:27,840 --> 00:22:29,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

300
00:22:29,700 --> 00:22:31,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm jealous.</font>

301
00:22:34,030 --> 00:22:35,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was that sound?</font>

302
00:22:43,630 --> 00:22:45,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This seems bad.</font>

303
00:23:08,010 --> 00:23:14,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>On the other side, even today</i></font>

304
00:23:14,140 --> 00:23:20,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Someone is unraveling, 
yet they still stand</i></font>

305
00:23:20,100 --> 00:23:26,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A stab to the chest, this loneliness</i></font>

306
00:23:26,010 --> 00:23:31,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Points and lines, 
breaking off and vanishing</i></font>

307
00:23:31,840 --> 00:23:34,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My shattered mask</i></font>

308
00:23:34,740 --> 00:23:37,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's more than I can bear</i></font>

309
00:23:37,820 --> 00:23:40,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I must keep on living</i></font>

310
00:23:40,810 --> 00:23:45,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tomorrow awaits to greet me</i></font>

311
00:23:45,600 --> 00:23:48,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's endless</i></font>

312
00:23:48,560 --> 00:23:51,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And so fragile</i></font>

313
00:23:51,130 --> 00:23:57,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is it better to believe 
hearts don't exist at all?</i></font>

314
00:23:57,360 --> 00:24:02,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Radiant and soft</i></font>

315
00:24:02,920 --> 00:24:04,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Was the hand</i></font>

316
00:24:04,630 --> 00:24:13,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I squeezed back on that day</i></font>

